@startuml

title SEDCM - Diagrama de Arquitectura (Actualizado)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam wrapWidth 220

actor "Operador" as operador

node "Docker Compose" {
  package "Simuladores" {
    [cAdvisor Bridge\n(simulators/cadvisor-bridge)] as cadvisor
    [Environment Simulator\n(simulators/environment)] as envsim
  }

  queue "Mosquitto\nMQTT Broker" as mqtt

  component "Backend\nFastAPI + Rules Engine\n(backend/app)" as backend
  database "PostgreSQL\ntelemetry_samples\nrack_state\naudit_log\nprocessed_message" as postgres

  component "Edge Executor\nDocker Adapter + Idempotency\n(edge-executor/app)" as edge
  component "Frontend Angular\n(frontend_angular)" as frontend
}

cloud "Docker API Local" as dockerapi

operador --> frontend : consulta dashboard
frontend --> backend : REST /racks y /racks/{zone}/{rack}

cadvisor --> mqtt : telemetria contenedores
envsim --> mqtt : telemetria ambiental

mqtt --> backend : consume telemetria
backend -> backend : fusion + validacion + reglas
backend --> postgres : persiste telemetria/estado/auditoria

backend --> mqtt : publica comando stop_critico
mqtt --> edge : consume comando

edge --> dockerapi : stop contenedor critico\nlabels dc.zone/dc.rack/dc.critical
edge --> mqtt : ACK ok|fail

mqtt --> backend : consume ACK/eventos
backend --> postgres : guarda ACK y trazabilidad

note right of backend
  Principios:
  - Seguridad termica primero
  - Desacoplamiento por MQTT
  - Trazabilidad y auditoria
  - Idempotencia
  - Histeresis anti-flapping
end note

@enduml
